><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/urYEbAb.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>#snow</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/8tFi7hy</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Luvlyquants]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Swimming with dolphins</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/4FBd7Y8</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8tI4mGW.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/4FBd7Y8</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[MedicalScience]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>USA Food and Italian Vomit.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/D1Frjlf</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/oqjE8QD.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Sauce :P https://www.instagram.com/p/C_0rKRVsaWl/</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/D1Frjlf</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[BenntheNinja]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I'm NOT famous (but I hang with famous people) Part 1</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/YlMn7hi</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Hw3h3y6.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Going through pics and I thought I'd share a few of my favourites from the last few years ... 

I was signing comics at Golden Apple in 2023 and the owner asks if I want to meet someone in the back ... SAM JACKSON is picking up comics! 

I ask the owner if I'm allowed to have a picture with him. Sam turns to the owner, and (in the Jules from PULP FICTION voice) says, "Why are you asking THIS motherfucker?! I'M the one you're taking the picture with!"

I was kind of stunned and could barely muster a smile LOL But it was great to chat with a legend. He even asked for a signed copy of ARENA MODE!

Best. Day. Ever.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/saePaF6.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Co-created a comic with EVANESCENCE lead singer Amy Lee in 2023, and I met her backstage at her concert in Toronto. AMAZING to meet her and the band, who were so kind and welcoming. 

We signed some copies of the book, and took some photos.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/njwePnH.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>If you're into cosplayers you probably know ERICA FETT, who I absolutely LOVE! I try to hang out with her at every con we both attend.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ojjXier.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Tehani Farr is an INCREDIBLE artist. She's so talented and beautiful. Love her. If you're into fantasy art, definitely check out her work.

Her HEAVY METAL cover was amazing!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/43n4TPI.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>One of the most legendary comic book creators of all time, Walt Simonson. We've never worked on a project together, but who knows what the future holds?

Fun fact: on his THOR run, he created both Beta Ray Bill AND Frog Thor!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Ze9OVnV.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And one of the sweetest people I know (and cosplayer for my BARBARELLA comic series) Rachie, aka 'Faces by Rachie'. She's a megastar at comic cons -- I did a signing with her at NYCC and the fans were rabid!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KSwHoUK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Apologies if you hate selfies ... to make up for it, here is a SHELFIE.

Jareth wishes you a wonderful weekend. xox

Love and hugs,
Blake xoxo</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/YlMn7hi</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[BlakeNorthcott]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Technology in the 21st century is getting scary realistic</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/gpYni1q</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/cfYIPsO.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/gpYni1q</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[XYOjiL]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Limit.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/LBzVYa4</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MhrZzPE.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/LBzVYa4</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[sleeperkid]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>The perfect headline</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/zW4GMZI</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/hZjkkb4.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/zW4GMZI</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Slayage]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>It must be a Weasley.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/ynAFPjM</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/aY3sJfC.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/ynAFPjM</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[MayMyEnemiesLiveLong]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>So cut the crap, Trump.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Ptb6Fap</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3QqaIB0.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Ptb6Fap</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[NotAUserName69]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Because, you know....</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/NQHfkAr</l